title: Wait What Did I Just Find LOL
body:
Okay okay.

So for a while, I have no idea why, not sure who's end it was on, Boards were loading stupid slow for me. I dont know why-- other sites were fine save for I think one other, but Boards were loading fine for a friend so I dont know what was up. Really weird but sometimes it happens. I even tried clearing my cache.

Well as I'd refresh the page again and again, I'd get different results.

Sometimes, it wouldn't load fully. Quite a few times the pages were just messed up.

Sometimes, failed connection page. 

But one time...

And note. I did not get a chance to click it; I refreshed without thinking or maybe it auto-refreshed I dont know/remember.

Anyhow...

What...

What is number 13 lol.
